            <lg xml:id="TK920">
<l>irumaṉap peṇṭiruṅ kaḷḷuṅ kavaṟum </l>
<l>tirunīkkap paṭṭār toṭarpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Treacherous women, liquor, and gambling are the associates of such as have forsaken by Fortune.</l>
